CHANGES IN VERSION 1.5.0
------------------------------

NEW FEATURES

    o 'opls' is now an S4 class: please use the accessors e.g. 'getScoreMN(oplsModel)' instead of 'oplsModel$scoreMN', or 'getScoreMN(oplsModel, orthoL = TRUE)' instead of 'oplsModel$orthoScoreMN'
    o The full list of accessors is: getLoadingMN, getScoreMN, getVipVn, getWeightMN (all with the orthoL argument), in addition to getSummaryDF, getPcaVarVn, getSubsetVi
    o Please see the vignette and documentation for examples    
    

